Value: Keypath Education International, Inc. designs, develops, and delivers career-relevant online education solutions in North America, Australia, Malaysia, the United Kingdom, and internationally. Its services include design and development of program courses; marketing of program courses to prospective students; recruitment and retention of students during enrollment; and placement services, as well as market research services to postgraduate education market. The company was founded in 2014 and is based in Schaumburg, Illinois. Keypath Education International, Inc. is a subsidiary of AVI Mezz Co., LP.
